Hi

User API clients are available in Python and JavaScript under `api/`.

Python usage:

```
from api.user_api import UserApi, UserApiConfig

api = UserApi(UserApiConfig(base_url="https://example.com", auth_token="token"))
users = api.list_users(page=1, per_page=20)
user = api.get_user(123)
created = api.create_user({"name": "Alice"})
updated = api.update_user(123, {"name": "Alice Updated"})
api.delete_user(123)
```

JavaScript usage (Node 18+ or browser):

```
import UserApi from './api/userApi.js'

const api = new UserApi('https://example.com', { authToken: 'token' })
const users = await api.listUsers({ page: 1, perPage: 20 })
const user = await api.getUser(123)
const created = await api.createUser({ name: 'Alice' })
const updated = await api.updateUser(123, { name: 'Alice Updated' })
await api.deleteUser(123)
```
